{"tid":502868,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「玩具撚」高比最想抱的腿是占士，潮人迷該何去何從？","createTime":"2017-12-18T10:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T14:13:12.000Z","uid":623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c217b98f56b81b76a621d08681dc9d50e7e003f","tid":502868,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"在明天進行的 Los Angeles Lakers 主場對陣 Golden State Warriors 的比賽中，將會舉辦 Laker 傳奇球員 Kobe Bryant 的球衣退役儀式，而他也將成為 NBA 歷史上唯一一位退役兩個號碼的球員。而在最近播出的一檔播客節目中，Kobe 表示讓他在巔峰期選擇一位球員做隊友，他會選擇 LeBron James。作為後 Michael Jordan 時期最偉大的兩位球員，Kobe 和 LeBron 各自擁有輝煌的生涯履歷和分佈在全球的無數球迷，雖然從未在總決賽的舞台上相遇，但兩人的競爭關係一直是 NBA 的最大賣點。在談到最適合自己的球員時，<span style=\"color: red;\">Kobe 表示：「我認爲最適合我的球員是 LeBron，他是一位天生的傳球組織者，而我是一名天生的終結者，我認爲這兩種風格對於雙方來說都是一個很好的補充。」</span><br />\n<br />\n其實兩人曾並肩作戰，代表美國隊征戰過 2008 年和 2012 年奧運會，並成功帶領「夢之隊」獲得兩枚金牌，如今再想重現這個讓人聞風喪膽的「雙王」組合，大家只能在遊戲中去實現了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/kobe-bryant-lebron-james-dream-teammate?utm_source=facebook%28paid%29&amp;utm_campaign=facebook-paid&amp;utm_medium=social\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2017%2F12%2Fkobe-bryant-lebron-james-dream-teammate%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%2528paid%2529%26utm_campaign%3Dfacebook-paid%26utm_medium%3Dsocial&d=z4J2ajRam%2B%2F7icYaYlpPXFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=49794a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/kobe-bryant-lebron-james-dream-teammate?utm_source=facebook%28paid%29&amp;utm_campaign=facebook-paid&amp;utm_medium=social</a><br />\n<br />\n一直占狗占狗咁追住吾皇來屌既狗鼻飯點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4e86e0560f0dc10ec43e43d8d8ed0a78c9f5d0","tid":502868,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"潮狗不願面對"},{"pid":"72c85ee45d8c5752ec56a305b979507e7809878d","tid":502868,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"潮人迷何去何從<img src=\"/assets/faces